{"id":81,"date":"2017-07-04T08:12:29","date_gmt":"2017-07-04T08:12:29","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/?p=81"},"modified":"2017-07-04T08:13:13","modified_gmt":"2017-07-04T08:13:13","slug":"kham-pha-hon-dao-nghe-thuat-naoshima","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/dulich.webtudong8giay.com\/kham-pha-hon-dao-nghe-thuat-naoshima\/","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt Naoshima"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>\u0110\u1ea3o Naoshima<\/strong> n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i kh\u01a1i b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n ph\u00eda nam t\u1ec9nh <strong>Kagawa<\/strong>, thu\u1ed9c v\u00f9ng bi\u1ec3n Seto. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn Naoshima \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn qu\u1ea3 b\u00ed ng\u00f4 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 Yayoi Kusama thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u2013 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4061\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/luu-ban-nhap-tu-dong-81.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-1.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-1-300x168.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-1-768x431.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea3o Naoshima \" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Naoshima c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng m\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 B\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng Benesse House, B\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng Lee Ufan, B\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt Chichu, ANDO MUSEUM. C\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0i tr\u00ed tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o khi\u1ebfn n\u00f3 tr\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4062\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/luu-ban-nhap-tu-dong-81-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-2.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-2-300x199.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-2-768x510.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea3o Naoshima \" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00ean <strong>\u0111\u1ea3o Naoshima<\/strong>, ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng l\u1edbn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Nh\u00e0 Ngh\u1ec7 Thu\u1eadt, do \u0111\u00f3 du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba thong th\u1ea3 d\u1ea1o ph\u1ed1 v\u1eeba ng\u1eafm c\u00e1c t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean tr\u00f9 ph\u00fa n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng quanh chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00fd th\u00fa nh\u01b0 trekking (\u0111i b\u1ed9 th\u00e1m hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i), t\u1eafm bi\u1ec3n\u2026 B\u1ebfn c\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 c\u1eeda ng\u00f5 giao th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea3o Naoshima n\u00ean xung quanh c\u1ea3ng Miyanoura c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, ti\u1ec7m \u0103n, c\u01a1 s\u1edf d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Rental car (\u00f4 t\u00f4 thu\u00ea), v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 tr\u1ecd.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4063\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/luu-ban-nhap-tu-dong-81-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-3.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-3-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-3-768x512.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ea3o Naoshima \" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o l\u00e0 \u00f4 t\u00f4, xe bu\u00fdt ho\u1eb7c xe \u0111\u1ea1p thu\u00ea. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i v\u00f2ng quanh \u0111\u1ea3o nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n th\u00ec xe bu\u00fdt v\u00e0 \u00f4 t\u00f4 thu\u00ea l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t th\u00ec xe \u0111\u1ea1p thu\u00ea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean hay d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1edf <strong>Naoshima<\/strong> <strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<\/strong> r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng n\u00ean h\u00e3y l\u01b0u \u00fd trang b\u1ecb c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ch\u1ed1ng say n\u1eafng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4064\" src=\"http:\/\/dulich.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/luu-ban-nhap-tu-dong-81-3.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\u0110\u1ea3o-Naoshima-4.jpg 800w, http:\/\/avitour.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/\